Class EventBusSimulationActionStatusEventReporter

java.lang.Object
  shadowman.simulation.status.EventBusSimulationActionStatusEventReporter
All Implemented Interfaces:
StatusReporter<SimulationStatusEvent>
public class EventBusSimulationActionStatusEventReporter
extends Object
implements StatusReporter<SimulationStatusEvent>

StatusReporter implementation accepting SimulationStatusEvent defining reporting behavior/frequency by evaluation of IncrementingStatusThresholds.hasBeenMet(shadowman.simulation.status.StatusProvider.Status). Once it has been determined that a reporting threshold has been met, a single SimulationStatusEvent is published via the provided EventBus.
